==Standings==
{{2026 FIFA World Cup group tables|Group K}}

In the [[2026 FIFA World Cup knockout stage#Round of 32|round of 32]]:<ref name="regulations"/>
* The winner of Group K will advance to play the third-placed team of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group D|Group D]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group E|Group E]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group I|Group I]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group J|Group J]], or [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group L|Group L]].
* The runner-up of Group K will advance to play the runner-up of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group L|Group L]].
* The third-placed team of Group K might advance to play the winner of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group L|Group L]] (if one of the [[2026 FIFA World Cup#Ranking of third-placed teams|eight best third-placed teams]] from the group stage).

